(1)
Westchester Avenue, north side, east from Olmstead Avenue. The frame dwelling is at the N.W. corner of Unionport Road.
April 10, 1938
P. L. Sperr
(2)
The same, a month later. also shown is the elevated structure
of the I.R.T. subway line.
May 10, 1938
P. L. Sperr
